WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:01.920
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.920 --> 00:00:03.063
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.063 --> 00:00:05.120
Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:07.920
Well, there is a lot going on right now, isn't there, baby?

00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:12.160
A major earthquake took place in Thailand, 7.

00:00:12.160 --> 00:00:12.891
7.

00:00:23.240 --> 00:00:23.650
And so far, they say 100,000 people they think have perished.

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:26.864
There's rubble on everybody.

00:00:26.864 --> 00:00:30.739
So, we need to pray for them today.

00:00:30.739 --> 00:00:38.250
That's one of the things we're going to lift up: that they would find the survivors and help find them quickly.

00:00:43.931 --> 00:00:44.320
You know, there are people buried underneath that rubble and all the debris.

00:00:53.430 --> 00:00:56.389
And I'm praying that they'll have rescue dogs, whatever they have, to find these people that are still alive, and that the people that are alive will be safe wherever they're at.

00:00:56.389 --> 00:00:59.040
This is a very, very serious situation.

00:01:03.714 --> 00:01:05.286
And you know, y'all, a lot of people say, 'Hey, Brandon, you prophesied.

00:01:05.286 --> 00:01:08.520
' Yes, I talked about this.

00:01:08.520 --> 00:01:13.560
This is what the Lord showed me was coming back a couple weeks ago.

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:19.919
And he told us, he said, 'Great earthquakes were going to start to take place.

00:01:19.919 --> 00:01:24.350
As labor pains upon a woman, so will it be.

00:01:30.919 --> 00:01:31.199
We're seeing the labor pains intensify.

00:01:31.199 --> 00:01:35.560
' And he told me they were going to intensify, folks.

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:50.312
And he said, 'Now, when I told you all we prayed last time, I saw that you could not go horizontal in your eyes in the flesh because of what we're going to see.

00:01:50.312 --> 00:02:13.476
' Because in the natural, if you are looking at what I have seen coming, if you're looking at going horizontal, it will have the tendency to try to get you in fear because of what we're going to see, because so many things are going to start to escalate.

00:02:26.444 --> 00:02:27.067
And he told us major earthquakes were going to start to take place.

00:02:27.067 --> 00:02:28.311
Major.

00:02:28.311 --> 00:02:32.977
And it would not be these little 5.

00:02:32.977 --> 00:02:33.769
0 earthquakes.

00:02:35.199 --> 00:02:52.411
I saw great earthquakes that would start to take place and they would happen in the sea, and I saw the sea opening and I saw the gases coming up and I saw the deep-sea fish—this would be a major sign that when we would see fish we've never seen before.

00:02:52.411 --> 00:03:15.226
Signs of fish that we've never seen before dying and washing up on the shore or fleeing the area and coming up higher out of the deep waters, trying to get away from what's happening on the ocean floor, because the Lord showed me there would be major things taking place on the ocean floor.

00:03:15.919 --> 00:03:17.433
And I saw tsunamis.

00:03:20.160 --> 00:03:21.959
I saw the one going into Alaska again.

00:03:21.959 --> 00:03:25.020
I saw that one.

00:03:25.020 --> 00:03:28.239
I've told you all about that.

00:03:42.120 --> 00:03:42.480
I told you all about the ones taking place in Japan.

00:03:42.480 --> 00:03:52.689
I've told you about the earthquakes in a lot of places, but it was more than that.

00:03:52.689 --> 00:03:54.910
It was about volcanoes.

00:03:54.910 --> 00:04:05.610
And I warned you about Italy and a major earthquake taking place in Italy and a tsunami wave coming in there.

00:04:14.710 --> 00:04:17.383
And so, like I said, for all the things and all the warnings that I'm warning you all about, he said this was not something that was man.

00:04:17.383 --> 00:04:20.000
This part was not something man-made.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:21.943
It's the earth groaning.

00:04:21.943 --> 00:04:23.893
It's the earth shaking.

00:04:23.893 --> 00:04:32.092
There's going to be major things happening in the earth because it is having birth pains.

00:04:32.759 --> 00:04:35.473
And we're going to see it because why?

00:04:35.473 --> 00:04:37.302
Jesus Christ is coming.

00:04:37.302 --> 00:04:38.415
Bottom line.

00:04:38.415 --> 00:04:42.636
And we're getting ready to step into the tribulation period.

00:04:44.422 --> 00:04:49.190
I believe the rapture of the church is right at our doorstep and most people are still asleep.

00:04:53.240 --> 00:04:59.097
And that's why he told us, not last prayer or the prayer before, whatever it was, he said, 'I'm going for the ones in the backfield.

00:04:59.097 --> 00:05:03.980
I'm coming for the revival for the ones in the backfield.

00:05:03.980 --> 00:05:09.240
' Brandon, I'm leaving the ninety-nine to go after the one.

00:05:09.240 --> 00:05:11.680
And most people are going, 'Brandon, really?

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:13.583
' No.

00:05:13.583 --> 00:05:17.889
Seriously, God loves you and he's coming after you.

00:05:17.889 --> 00:05:23.120
He said, 'Satan has come after the kids, but Brandon, I'm coming after him harder.

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:26.857
I'm coming after this youth generation.

00:05:26.857 --> 00:05:32.206
I'm coming after the ones that seem like there was no hope.

00:05:32.206 --> 00:05:35.279
I'm coming after the unlovely.

00:05:35.279 --> 00:05:37.724
' Do you understand, folks?

00:05:37.724 --> 00:05:41.275
God is a God that is not a loser.

00:05:41.275 --> 00:05:43.834
He's a victorious God.

00:05:54.670 --> 00:05:55.100
And we are on the victory side.

00:06:00.667 --> 00:06:01.013
And I'm telling you, God is coming after your unsaved loved ones.

00:06:06.608 --> 00:06:06.960
And they're going to have that road to Damascus experience.

00:06:06.960 --> 00:06:09.600
They're going to have that shaking to awaken.

00:06:12.137 --> 00:06:13.680
And I believe we're not going to go in the rapture defeated.

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:20.493
We're going victorious and we're going without spot or wrinkle.

00:06:30.326 --> 00:06:30.771
And we're going to go with the healing revival and demonstrations and manifestations of the glory of God like we've never seen before.

00:06:30.771 --> 00:06:35.640
But yes, we are going to see.

00:06:35.640 --> 00:06:39.819
I told you it's like focusing on a quarter.

00:06:39.819 --> 00:06:41.380
There's two sides.

00:06:44.640 --> 00:06:48.639
The quarter is really thin, but both sides are very different from the other.

00:06:49.972 --> 00:06:54.860
And that's the way it's going to be.

00:06:54.860 --> 00:07:07.469
You're going to either focus on the light or you're going to focus on the darkness because things are going to go gross darkness.

00:07:26.971 --> 00:07:27.348
So much so, the darkness that I saw that was coming was so dark that it was tangible.

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:31.640
It was just like it was in Egypt.

00:07:31.640 --> 00:07:33.599
Darkness that you could feel.

00:07:33.599 --> 00:07:42.903
I don't know about you, but I've never felt darkness so dark that you can feel it.

00:07:42.903 --> 00:07:45.965
How do you—I mean, that is overwhelming darkness.

00:07:46.890 --> 00:07:53.099
The light's going to get lighter and the dark's going to get darker.

00:08:05.813 --> 00:08:06.159
But the glorious church is going to rise up like the Tommy Hicks vision.

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:14.240
And I believe like Jesus said to us in the last two or three prayer times ago: 'Who's going to say yes?

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:17.538
Who's going to say yes?

00:08:17.538 --> 00:08:23.510
' So here we see another thing: Zelensky saying, 'We're not going to forgive the United States.

00:08:23.510 --> 00:08:28.418
We're not going to pay back the United States debts.

00:08:28.418 --> 00:08:32.009
' And we see him saying, 'We want aid.

00:08:43.271 --> 00:08:43.599
We want more missiles.

00:08:48.408 --> 00:08:48.692
We want this stuff.

00:08:48.692 --> 00:08:58.240
' And I said, I told you all there will be—that man is a very dark man.

00:09:01.360 --> 00:09:04.480
And I'm telling you, there's going to be a false—I feel it in my spirit still.

00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:07.467
I'm still praying over this.

00:09:23.400 --> 00:09:23.820
And it's something we all should be praying over: a false flag event, a provoking of trying to poke the bear.

00:09:23.820 --> 00:09:33.017
I'm telling you all, we need to be praying that they don't try to poke the bear—poking the bear to do something very drastic.

00:09:37.115 --> 00:09:44.719
And I said there is a distraction over here while the Houthis and all this stuff going on for what Iran is not wanting to be uncovered.

00:09:45.680 --> 00:09:47.600
And there will be an uncovering.

00:09:52.530 --> 00:10:06.183
And I've seen the United States of America striking Iran, Israel striking Iran, and it brought on great anti-Semitism, more than what we've ever seen before in America, protesting the lives that they'd say were taken in Iran in the days ahead.

00:10:06.183 --> 00:10:23.519
A major escalation of war in the Middle East for what I have seen coming with Turkey going alongside Syria in the days ahead and them trying to basically be like a big brother to Syria more than what we've ever seen before.

00:10:23.519 --> 00:10:27.657
Then we will see—I've seen in the spirit more about Iran.

00:10:27.657 --> 00:10:29.244
So we'll see.

00:10:29.244 --> 00:10:31.360
We're praying over that stuff.

00:10:31.360 --> 00:10:35.680
So we pray that it does not happen.

00:10:52.400 --> 00:10:52.747
But I'm telling you, we will see an increase of war and rumors of war in these days ahead.

00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:59.623
And we are going to see plagues, pestilence, and we're going to see these things, folks.

00:11:04.720 --> 00:11:05.120
The Bible said we would.

00:11:08.880 --> 00:11:09.230
The Bible said we would.

00:11:09.230 --> 00:11:13.147
But where are we supposed to keep our eyes?

00:11:13.147 --> 00:11:16.319
On him.

00:11:16.319 --> 00:11:17.039
Yep.

00:11:17.039 --> 00:11:17.760
Why?

00:11:17.760 --> 00:11:19.530
Because our redemption's drawing nigh.

00:11:22.016 --> 00:11:22.248
And he said to be hearing him.

00:11:22.248 --> 00:11:29.480
If you are not listening to the Lord, you could go in the wrong place at the wrong time and not make it.

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:34.301
But if you are following the Holy Spirit like a snapping of a finger, boom, boom, boom.

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:39.480
And you're listening to him, being filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit, you will always be protected.

00:11:39.480 --> 00:11:40.679
You are his beloved.

00:11:40.679 --> 00:11:48.720
But if you step out of sync with him, it's an opportunity for the devil to try to take you out before you're supposed to go home.

00:11:54.060 --> 00:11:54.310
And I refuse to let the devil do that.

00:11:54.310 --> 00:12:07.748
We are going to be in sync with the Father, listening to his voice and the stranger's voice we will not follow, and being like that heartbeat, following as he dances, as he leads in prayer, we will follow.

00:12:07.748 --> 00:12:16.583
But we're seeing the things happen on the news is what I'm trying to tell you.

00:12:16.583 --> 00:12:22.080
We had the first major earthquake and 100,000 people.

00:12:22.080 --> 00:12:22.984
That's terrible.

00:12:22.984 --> 00:12:26.206
We pray for the victims.

00:12:26.206 --> 00:12:29.080
We pray for the people.

00:12:29.080 --> 00:12:33.320
But I'm telling you, there's more coming.

00:12:43.415 --> 00:12:43.830
And it will happen with the oceans.

00:12:43.830 --> 00:12:51.664
We know that we are looking because we know our redemption is drawing nigh.

00:12:51.664 --> 00:12:53.648
We're looking to the skies.

00:12:53.648 --> 00:12:58.540
But this is what I saw in prayer yesterday.

00:12:58.540 --> 00:13:04.170
I saw Jesus standing right here and he was looking at a brook.

00:13:04.170 --> 00:13:12.040
It was a stream and there were mountains on this side like a valley.

00:13:21.320 --> 00:13:21.670
I could see rock ledges and there was a stream running through like a snake stream.

00:13:28.169 --> 00:13:28.480
It looked like it was curvy and it ran through, and Jesus was watching.

00:13:48.600 --> 00:13:48.930
I saw people on both sides come up to the water and start lapping up the water.

00:13:48.930 --> 00:13:54.010
Some of them were very dignified in the way they got on their knees.

00:13:54.010 --> 00:14:05.280
They had their nice clothes on and they didn't want to look like they were going to dirty themselves.

00:14:05.280 --> 00:14:15.813
They got up there and they just barely squatted down and they cupped their hands and they brought the water up to them.

00:14:15.813 --> 00:14:23.600
But some of the people that went up to the water were desperate and they were just like, 'I am so thirsty.

00:14:23.600 --> 00:14:26.870
I have to have this water.

00:14:26.870 --> 00:14:29.325
' And they were undignified.

00:14:35.227 --> 00:14:35.449
They did not look like they had a lot going for them.

00:14:35.449 --> 00:14:37.220
Their clothes weren't as nice.

00:14:37.550 --> 00:14:40.467
They didn't look like they were real clean.

00:14:42.409 --> 00:14:43.760
They were desperate and out of the desperation they were drinking the water.

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:48.776
They were trying to fill themselves up with that water all they could as fast as they could.

00:14:59.440 --> 00:15:01.154
You knew the other people were desperate and thirsty but they didn't want to display themselves like that.

00:15:03.399 --> 00:15:10.320
I saw the Lord and I said, 'Lord, what are you doing in my prayer time yesterday?

00:15:10.320 --> 00:15:14.440
' and he said, 'I'm watching to see who's the thirstiest.

00:15:14.440 --> 00:15:20.310
I'm watching to see who's going to come with me to the greater glory.

00:15:20.310 --> 00:15:23.499
Who can be used for the greater glory?

00:15:23.499 --> 00:15:25.880
I'm watching how they're drinking.

00:15:25.880 --> 00:15:33.760
' So, this is the scripture the Lord gave to me when I was in the vision.

00:15:33.760 --> 00:15:38.580
Diana's going to read this and then we're going to go to another scripture the Lord gave me.

00:15:39.840 --> 00:15:46.240
And the Lord said to Gideon, 'The men are still too many.

00:15:46.240 --> 00:15:55.839
Bring them down to the water and I will test them for you there.

00:15:59.427 --> 00:16:12.457
And he of whom I say to you, 'This man shall go with you,' shall go with you.

00:16:22.148 --> 00:16:22.411
And he of whom I say to you, 'This man shall not go with you,' shall not go.

00:16:22.411 --> 00:16:26.068
' So he brought the men down to the water.

00:16:27.279 --> 00:16:36.720
And the Lord said to Gideon, 'Everyone who laps up the water with his tongue as a dog laps it, you shall set by himself.

00:16:36.720 --> 00:16:41.600
Likewise, everyone who bows down on his knees to drink.

00:16:41.600 --> 00:16:48.720
' And the number of those who lapped, putting their hand to their mouth, was 300 men.

00:16:55.652 --> 00:16:56.079
But the rest of the people bowed down upon their knees to drink the water.

00:16:56.079 --> 00:17:04.310
And the Lord said to Gideon, 'With the 300 men who lapped, I will deliver you and give the Midianites into your hand.

00:17:04.310 --> 00:17:09.149
Let all the others return every man to his home.

00:17:09.149 --> 00:17:16.823
' So basically, he was looking for the people who were undignified.

00:17:16.823 --> 00:17:22.219
He was looking for the people who were sold out and were really thirsty.

00:17:23.299 --> 00:17:25.360
They did not care about how they looked.

00:17:25.968 --> 00:17:27.271
They probably looked really dumb.

00:17:37.640 --> 00:17:37.860
They probably didn't look too educated.

00:17:37.860 --> 00:17:39.600
They just wanted the water.

00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:42.720
How desperate do you want the water?

00:17:47.831 --> 00:17:55.919
And the Lord said to me, 'I'm watching to see how my people are drinking to see the ones who I'm going to be able to take to the end-time glory.

00:17:55.919 --> 00:17:58.719
Who are the ones and how are they drinking?

00:17:58.719 --> 00:18:02.222
Do they care about what they look like?

00:18:02.222 --> 00:18:04.114
Are they sold out?

00:18:04.114 --> 00:18:06.320
Are they all in?

00:18:06.320 --> 00:18:10.823
Are they too worried about how they look in public?

00:18:10.823 --> 00:18:16.125
Or will I look embarrassed if I lay hands on the sick?

00:18:20.640 --> 00:18:27.154
And if he asks me to cast out a devil, is it convenient for me right now because that person over there might talk bad about me?

00:18:27.154 --> 00:18:38.480
I'm all in and I'm drinking that water with all I've got because I'm desperate just to please him.

00:18:38.480 --> 00:18:45.360
No matter what nobody else thinks, I am going to lap it up like a dog.

00:18:45.360 --> 00:18:47.880
' He just took 300.

00:18:47.880 --> 00:18:56.680
So, it doesn't take a lot for this end-time harvest.

00:18:56.680 --> 00:19:05.166
He's just looking for the ones who don't care about what everybody else thinks about them.

00:19:05.166 --> 00:19:10.240
He's just wanting somebody that wants just to drink.

00:19:12.720 --> 00:19:13.440
How desperate are you for the water?

00:19:13.440 --> 00:19:14.160
How thirsty?

00:19:14.160 --> 00:19:14.983
How hungry?

00:19:14.983 --> 00:19:16.613
That's what it's coming down to.

00:19:16.613 --> 00:19:22.300
Gideon's mighty men, the ones that went and defeated, were just sold out and they looked foolish.

00:19:32.987 --> 00:19:33.253
But God said, 'He's the one; you can use them.

00:19:33.253 --> 00:19:35.840
' The other guys are too dignified.

00:19:35.840 --> 00:19:43.646
So this is another scripture that we got about the drinking, letting the Holy Spirit use you.

00:19:49.066 --> 00:19:49.333
It's in John 7.

00:19:49.333 --> 00:20:04.968
Now on the final and most important day of the feast, Jesus stood and he cried in a loud voice, 'If any man is thirsty, let him come to me and drink.

00:20:04.968 --> 00:20:20.408
He who believes in me, who cleaves to and trusts in and relies on me, as the scripture has said, from his innermost being shall flow continuously springs and rivers of living water.

00:20:20.408 --> 00:20:24.640
' He who believes in me, who cleaves to and trusts in and relies on me.

00:20:24.640 --> 00:20:27.156
Cleaves to, trusts in, and relies on me.

00:20:27.156 --> 00:20:32.258
As the scripture has said, from his innermost being shall flow continuously springs and rivers of living water.

00:20:32.258 --> 00:20:37.440
Springs and rivers of living water that are coming out of the throne.

00:20:46.195 --> 00:20:46.617
And he's watching to see how you drink.

00:20:46.617 --> 00:20:51.840
This scripture right here is what he showed me.

00:20:51.840 --> 00:20:56.263
This is John 7, which is amazing.

00:21:10.009 --> 00:21:10.231
It goes along with Gideon and with the drinking.

00:21:10.231 --> 00:21:14.457
When you're praying in the spirit, you're coming to him for the drink.

00:21:26.719 --> 00:21:26.986
And as you're drinking from him, out of you flow the rivers.

00:21:26.986 --> 00:21:39.886
We're trying to dump that river out on everybody else because it's the anointing that destroys the yoke.

00:21:39.886 --> 00:21:58.359
But a lot of people go up to the river with a little straw and they try to drink with a little straw, filling themselves up, but they're trying to dump a bathtub outside of you.

00:21:58.359 --> 00:22:07.412
But you've only used a little straw to fill up the water drinking from him.

00:22:07.412 --> 00:22:11.451
We've got to become bigger drinkers.

00:22:11.451 --> 00:22:13.257
Drink from the well.

00:22:13.257 --> 00:22:21.060
Just like he said, 'I'm opening the caps of revival of the deeper water.

00:22:21.060 --> 00:22:25.493
' Remember the word I gave you all?

00:22:40.000 --> 00:22:40.284
It was Brother Hagin.

00:22:40.284 --> 00:23:08.540
They took a little bit of a cup and they drank a little of it, and Oral Roberts had a little cup of that revival, and Kathryn Kuhlman and all the ones in the tent revivals back in the early 1900s, like Jack Coe and all them.

00:23:08.540 --> 00:23:18.596
But the Lord said to me, 'Brandon, where I'm taking the body of Christ in these last days is in the deeper water.

00:23:20.024 --> 00:23:30.039
And you will not just go ankle deep, but you're going to go all the way down.

00:23:30.039 --> 00:23:53.050
' Remember when I told you I went to the throne room and he said, 'It's time for the body to go over the head,' because there was a fountain of water flowing down at the Father's throne and there was ankle-deep water, waist-deep water, and all the way down.

00:23:53.050 --> 00:23:55.129
It was the clearest crystal water I've ever seen.

00:23:55.129 --> 00:23:58.471
The pool of living water was flowing out of the throne and out of the Father.

00:23:58.924 --> 00:24:01.600
And he said, "Brandon, it's time to go to the deeper waters.

00:24:01.600 --> 00:24:03.000
" It's undignified, folks.

00:24:03.000 --> 00:24:12.130
It's losing yourself and not being dignified.

00:24:12.130 --> 00:24:27.060
It's being filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit for what he's wanting to do in these last days.

00:24:27.060 --> 00:24:31.860
Go to the deeper water where the Holy Ghost is at.

00:24:31.860 --> 00:24:35.840
Lose yourself in it.

00:24:35.840 --> 00:24:52.286
Not caring who's around you, dying to self—what we're always talking about—dying to self, being a vessel that God can use because you are filled and controlled by the Holy Spirit, being that river like Diana was talking about, getting to it and drinking.

00:25:03.629 --> 00:25:04.460
So, how do you drink, Diana?

00:25:04.460 --> 00:25:20.640
You have to open your mouth to drink, because you can be in a pool full of water and you can die of thirst if you don't open your mouth and drink, right?

00:25:40.617 --> 00:25:41.246
You can be all the way in that pool and totally die of thirst.

00:25:50.640 --> 00:25:59.280
You could be in ten-foot-deep water with your head all the way in it, but if you don't open your mouth and drink, you can die of thirst.

00:26:08.914 --> 00:26:09.245
You have to drink.

00:26:09.245 --> 00:26:10.516
Be a receiver.

00:26:10.516 --> 00:26:11.067
Receive.

00:26:11.067 --> 00:26:12.720
How do you receive?

00:26:12.720 --> 00:26:16.559
